trans-unit.source: Provides the <xref uid="langword_csharp_abstract" name="abstract" href=""></xref> base class for the listeners who monitor trace and debug output.
trans-unit.target: Gir den <xref uid="langword_csharp_abstract" name="abstract" href=""> </xref> basisklasse for lyttere som overvåker sporingen og feilsøke utdata.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The following table shows initial property values for an instance of <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser første egenskapsverdier for en forekomst av <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"></xref> class using the specified name as the listener.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av det angitte navnet som lytteren.

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the custom trace listener attributes defined in the application configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Henter Egendefinert sporings-lytteren attributtene som er definert i programmets konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: Classes that inherit from the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener> class can add custom attributes by overriding the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.GetSupportedAttributes%2A> method and returning a string array of custom attribute names.
trans-unit.target: Klasser som arver fra den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>klassen kan legge til egendefinerte attributter ved å overstyre den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.GetSupportedAttributes%2A>metoden og returnere en strengmatrise for egendefinert attributtnavn.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.GetSupportedAttributes%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>

trans-unit.source: The Attributes property identifies the custom attributes that are referenced in the application's configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen attributter identifiserer egendefinerte attributter som refereres til i programmets konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: For example, in the following configuration file excerpt the <xref:System.Diagnostics.DelimitedListTraceListener> custom attribute "delimiter" is referenced.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel i følgende konfigurasjon filen utdrag den <xref:System.Diagnostics.DelimitedListTraceListener>egendefinerte attributtet "Skilletegn" refereres.</xref:System.Diagnostics.DelimitedListTraceListener>

trans-unit.source: In this case, the Attributes property returns a <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringDictionary> containing the string "delimiter".
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet egenskapen attributter returnerer en <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringDictionary>som inneholder strengen "Skilletegn".</xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringDictionary>

trans-unit.source: ``` <listeners> <add name="delimitedListener" type="System.Diagnostics.DelimitedListTraceListener" delimiter=":" initializeData="delimitedOutput.txt" traceOutputOptions="ProcessId, DateTime" /> <remove name="Default" /> </listeners> ``` Unreferenced custom attributes are not enumerated.
trans-unit.target: ``` <listeners> <add name="delimitedListener" type="System.Diagnostics.DelimitedListTraceListener" delimiter=":" initializeData="delimitedOutput.txt" traceOutputOptions="ProcessId, DateTime" /> <remove name="Default" /> </listeners> ```Ubrukte egendefinerte attributter listes ikke.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.GetSupportedAttributes%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.GetSupportedAttributes%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.GetSupportedAttributes%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringDictionary"></xref> containing the custom attributes for the trace listener.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringDictionary"> </xref> som inneholder de egendefinerte attributtene for sporingslytteren for.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, closes the output stream so it no longer receives tracing or debugging output.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, lukkes utdata dataflyten slik at den ikke lenger mottar sporing eller feilsøking utdata.

trans-unit.source: Use this method when the output is going to a file, such as to the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TextWriterTraceListener>.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne metoden hvis utdataene skal til en fil som <xref:System.Diagnostics.TextWriterTraceListener>.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TextWriterTraceListener>

trans-unit.source: After a call to this method, you must reinitialize the object.
trans-unit.target: Etter et kall til denne metoden, må du initialisere objektet.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Calling Dispose allows the resources used by the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener> to be reallocated for other purposes.
trans-unit.target: Kaller avhending tillater ressursene som brukes av den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>til tildeles på nytt til andre formål.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>

trans-unit.source: For more information about Dispose, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om avhending [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir uforvaltede ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"> </xref> og eventuelt frigir administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Dispose%2A> method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles av offentlig <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Dispose%2A>metoden og <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metode.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: `Dispose` invokes the protected <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Dispose%2A> method with the `disposing` parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose`Aktiverer den beskyttede <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Dispose%2A>metoden med den `disposing` parameteren satt til `true`.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>aktiverer `Dispose` med `disposing` satt til `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the `disposing` parameter is `true`, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener> references.
trans-unit.target: Når den `disposing` parameteren er `true`, denne metoden Frigjør alle ressurser holdes av administrerte objekter som denne <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>referanser.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden starter den `Dispose` metode for hver referert objekt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre både administrerte og uforvaltede ressurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Emits an error message to the listener you create when you implement the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Avgir feilmeldingen for lytteren du oppretter når du implementerer den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The default behavior is to display the specified message in a message box when the application is running in a user-interface mode, and to the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener> instances in a <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Standard virkemåte er å vise den angitte meldingen i en melding når programmet kjører i brukergrensesnittet modus, og til den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>forekomster i en <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection>samling.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>

trans-unit.source: By default, the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> collection has an instance of a <xref:System.Diagnostics.DefaultTraceListener>.
trans-unit.target: Som standard <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection>samlingen inneholder en forekomst av en <xref:System.Diagnostics.DefaultTraceListener>.</xref:System.Diagnostics.DefaultTraceListener> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection>

trans-unit.source: You can customize this behavior by adding a <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener> to or removing one from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Du kan tilpasse dette problemet ved å legge til en <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>til eller fjerne en fra samlingen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>

trans-unit.source: A message to emit.
trans-unit.target: En melding utdata fra.

trans-unit.source: Emits an error message and a detailed error message to the listener you create when you implement the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Avgir feilmeldingen meldings- og en detaljert feilmelding for lytteren du oppretter når du implementerer den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The default behavior is to display the message and detailed message in a message box when the application is running in a user-interface mode, and to the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener> instances in a <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Standard virkemåte er å vise meldings- og detaljert melding i en melding når programmet kjører i brukergrensesnittet modus, og til den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>forekomster i en <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection>samling.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>

trans-unit.source: By default, the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> collection has an instance of a <xref:System.Diagnostics.DefaultTraceListener>.
trans-unit.target: Som standard <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection>samlingen inneholder en forekomst av en <xref:System.Diagnostics.DefaultTraceListener>.</xref:System.Diagnostics.DefaultTraceListener> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection>

trans-unit.source: You can customize this behavior by adding a <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener> to or removing one from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Du kan tilpasse dette problemet ved å legge til en <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>til eller fjerne en fra samlingen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>

trans-unit.source: A message to emit.
trans-unit.target: En melding utdata fra.

trans-unit.source: A detailed message to emit.
trans-unit.target: En detaljert melding utdata fra.

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the trace filter for the trace listener.
trans-unit.target: Får eller angir trace-filteret for sporingslytteren for.

trans-unit.source: A trace filter can be added to a trace listener to provide a layer of screening beyond that provided to the trace source by switches.
trans-unit.target: Filtere sporingen kan legges til en sporingen lytter å levere et lag med screeningen utover det som er angitt til datakilden for sporing av bytter.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventTypeFilter> can be added to a trace listener to control the event types that are output by the listener.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventTypeFilter>kan legges til en sporingen lytter til å kontrollere hendelsestypene er utdata av lytteren.</xref:System.Diagnostics.EventTypeFilter>

trans-unit.source: Listeners that are called because the switch criteria are met can query their filter, if present, to determine if a trace is to be sent to output.
trans-unit.target: Lyttere kalles fordi switch kriteriene oppfylles kan spørre deres filter, hvis det finnes for å finne ut om en sporing sendes til utdata.

trans-unit.source: An object derived from the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceFilter"></xref> base class.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som er avledet fra den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceFilter"> </xref> basisklasse.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, flushes the output buffer.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, Tømminger av utdatabufferen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the custom attributes supported by the trace listener.
trans-unit.target: Henter de egendefinerte attributtene som støttes av sporingslytteren for.

trans-unit.source: The default implementation for GetSupportedAttributes returns `null`.
trans-unit.target: Standardimplementering for GetSupportedAttributes returnerer `null`.

trans-unit.source: A string array naming the custom attributes supported by the trace listener, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if there are no custom attributes.
trans-unit.target: En strengmatrise navngi egendefinerte attributter støttes av sporingslytteren for, eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> Hvis det er ingen egendefinerte attributter.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the indent level.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir innrykksnivået.

trans-unit.source: The IndentLevel property represents the number of times that the indent specified by the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.IndentSize%2A> property is applied.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen IndentLevel representerer hvor mange ganger som innrykket angitt av den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.IndentSize%2A>egenskap brukes.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.IndentSize%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property is stored on per-thread/per-request basis.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er lagret på per-tråd/per-forespørsel basis.

trans-unit.source: The indent level.
trans-unit.target: Innrykksnivået.

trans-unit.source: The default is zero.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er null.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the number of spaces in an indent.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir antallet mellomrom i innrykket.

trans-unit.source: The property is stored on per-thread/per-request basis.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen er lagret på per-tråd/per-forespørsel basis.

trans-unit.source: The number of spaces in an indent.
trans-unit.target: Antall mellomrom i innrykket.

trans-unit.source: The default is four spaces.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er fire mellomrom.

trans-unit.source: Set operation failed because the value is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: Set-operasjon mislyktes fordi verdien er mindre enn null.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the trace listener is thread safe.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om sporingslytteren for er tråd trygt.

trans-unit.source: The value of IsThreadSafe is used to determine whether to use a global lock when writing to the listener.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for IsThreadSafe brukes til å finne ut om du vil bruke en global Lås under skriving til lytteren.

trans-unit.source: If the value of IsThreadSafe is `false`, the global lock is used regardless of the value of <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.UseGlobalLock%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien IsThreadSafe `false`, globale låsen brukes uavhengig av verdien for <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.UseGlobalLock%2A>.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.UseGlobalLock%2A>

trans-unit.source: The global lock is not used only if the value of IsThreadSafe is `true` and the value of <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.UseGlobalLock%2A> is `false`.
trans-unit.target: Globale låsen ikke brukes bare hvis verdien for IsThreadSafe `true` verdien av <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.UseGlobalLock%2A>er `false`.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.UseGlobalLock%2A>

trans-unit.source: The default behavior is to use the global lock whenever writing to the listener.
trans-unit.target: Standard virkemåte er å bruke den globale låse når skriving for lytteren.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the trace listener is thread safe; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis sporingslytteren for er tråd trygt; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a name for this <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et navn for dette <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The name can be used to organize and access listeners in a <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Navnet kan brukes til å organisere og få tilgang til lyttere i en <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection>samling.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection>

trans-unit.source: A name for this <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Et navn for dette <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Standarden er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether to indent the output.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om innrykk utdataene.

trans-unit.source: **Note** The <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.WriteIndent%2A> method, called by the <xref:System.Diagnostics.DefaultTraceListener> and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TextWriterTraceListener> classes, sets the NeedIndent property value to `false` to prevent later, unnecessary indents.
trans-unit.target: **Obs** den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.WriteIndent%2A>metoden kalles av den <xref:System.Diagnostics.DefaultTraceListener>og <xref:System.Diagnostics.TextWriterTraceListener>klasser, angir egenskapsverdien NeedIndent til `false` å hindre at senere unødvendige innrykk.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TextWriterTraceListener> </xref:System.Diagnostics.DefaultTraceListener> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.WriteIndent%2A>

trans-unit.source: You must set the NeedIndent property to `true` each time you wish to indent trace output.
trans-unit.target: Du må sette egenskapen NeedIndent til `true` hver gang du vil innrykk Sporingsutdata.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the output should be indented; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis utdataene skal være innrykkede; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Writes trace information, a data object and event information to the listener specific output.
trans-unit.target: Skriver sporingen informasjon, en objektet og hendelsen metadatainformasjon til lytteren bestemte utdata.

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > This method is not intended to be called directly by application code but by members of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace>, and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> classes to write trace data to output.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT]> Denne metoden skal ikke kalles direkte etter kode for programmet, men av medlemmer av den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace>, og <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>klasser å skrive sporingsdata til å sende.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug>

trans-unit.source: The default implementation writes the `eventCache`, `source`, `eventType` and `id` parameters in the header and footer of the trace.
trans-unit.target: Standard implementering skriver den `eventCache`, `source`, `eventType` og `id` parametere i topp- og bunntekstene på sporingen.

trans-unit.source: The `data` parameter is written as the body of the trace message.
trans-unit.target: Den `data` parameteren skrives som trace-meldingsteksten.

trans-unit.source: The `ToString` method of the data object is used to convert the object to a <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: Den `ToString` dataobjektet til å konvertere objektet til <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache"></xref> object that contains the current process ID, thread ID, and stack trace information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache"> </xref> objekt som inneholder gjeldende prosess-ID tråd-ID og stable sporingsinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: A name used to identify the output, typically the name of the application that generated the trace event.
trans-unit.target: Et navn som brukes til å identifisere output, vanligvis navnet på programmet som genererte sporingshendelsen.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType"></xref> values specifying the type of event that has caused the trace.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType"> </xref> verdier som angir hvilken type hendelse som har forårsaket sporingen.

trans-unit.source: A numeric identifier for the event.
trans-unit.target: En numerisk identifikator for hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: The trace data to emit.
trans-unit.target: Sporingsdata utdata fra.

trans-unit.source: Writes trace information, an array of data objects and event information to the listener specific output.
trans-unit.target: Skriver Spor informasjon, en rekke Dataobjekter og hendelsesinformasjon til lytteren bestemte utdata.

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > This method is not intended to be called directly by application code but by members of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace>, and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> classes to write trace data to output.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT]> Denne metoden skal ikke kalles direkte etter kode for programmet, men av medlemmer av den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace>, og <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>klasser å skrive sporingsdata til å sende.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug>

trans-unit.source: The default implementation writes the values of the `source`, `eventType` and `id` parameters as a header.
trans-unit.target: Standard implementering skriver verdiene i den `source`, `eventType` og `id` parametere som et hode.

trans-unit.source: The data objects are converted to strings using the `ToString` method of each object.
trans-unit.target: Dataobjekter konverteres til strenger ved hjelp av den `ToString` -metoden til hver enkelt objekt.

trans-unit.source: The `eventCache` data is written as a footer, the nature of the output data being dependent on the value of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceOutputOptions%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den `eventCache` data blir skrevet som en bunntekst, ettersom utdata er avhengig av verdien for den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceOutputOptions%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceOutputOptions%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache"></xref> object that contains the current process ID, thread ID, and stack trace information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache"> </xref> objekt som inneholder gjeldende prosess-ID tråd-ID og stable sporingsinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: A name used to identify the output, typically the name of the application that generated the trace event.
trans-unit.target: Et navn som brukes til å identifisere output, vanligvis navnet på programmet som genererte sporingshendelsen.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType"></xref> values specifying the type of event that has caused the trace.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType"> </xref> verdier som angir hvilken type hendelse som har forårsaket sporingen.

trans-unit.source: A numeric identifier for the event.
trans-unit.target: En numerisk identifikator for hendelsen.

trans-unit.target: En matrise av objekter utdata fra som data.

trans-unit.source: Writes trace and event information to the listener specific output.
trans-unit.target: Skriver sporing og hendelsen informasjon til lytteren bestemte utdata.

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > This method is not intended to be called directly by application code but by members of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace>, and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> classes to write trace data to output.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT]> Denne metoden skal ikke kalles direkte etter kode for programmet, men av medlemmer av den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace>, og <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>klasser å skrive sporingsdata til å sende.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the trace output options.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir sporingen alternativer for utdata.

trans-unit.source: The TraceOutputOptions property determines the optional content of trace output.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen TraceOutputOptions angir valgfrie innholdet i Sporingsutdata.

trans-unit.source: The property can be set in the configuration file or programmatically during execution to include additional data specifically for a section of code.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen kan angis i konfigurasjonsfilen eller programmatisk under kjøring av å ta med ekstra data spesielt for en del av koden.

trans-unit.source: For example, you can set the TraceOutputOptions property for the console trace listener to <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceOptions?displayProperty=fullName> to add call stack information to the trace output.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel angi egenskapen TraceOutputOptions for konsollen sporingslytteren til <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceOptions?displayProperty=fullName>å legge til kall Stakkinformasjon i Sporingsutdata.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceOptions?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceOptions> enumeration is not used by the following classes and methods: - The <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener> class, because it can cause a large volume of data to be written to the log.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceOptions>opplisting ikke brukes av følgende klasser og metoder:- <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener>klasse, fordi det kan føre til at store mengder data skrives til loggen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogTraceListener> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceOptions>

trans-unit.source: - The `Write` and `WriteLine` methods of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.ConsoleTraceListener>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.DefaultTraceListener>, and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TextWriterTraceListener> classes.
trans-unit.target: - `Write` Og `WriteLine` metoder for den <xref:System.Diagnostics.ConsoleTraceListener>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.DefaultTraceListener>, og <xref:System.Diagnostics.TextWriterTraceListener>klasser.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TextWriterTraceListener> </xref:System.Diagnostics.DefaultTraceListener> </xref:System.Diagnostics.ConsoleTraceListener>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Write%2A> and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.WriteLine%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener> class when they are not overridden in a derived class.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Write%2A>Og <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.WriteLine%2A>metoder for <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener>klassen når de ikke overstyres i en avledet klasse.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.WriteLine%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Write%2A>

trans-unit.source: Call this method if <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.NeedIndent%2A> is `true` when you are overriding the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.Write%2A> and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.WriteLine%2A> methods.

trans-unit.source: By default, this method uses blank spaces for indentation.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden brukes som standard mellomrom innrykk.

trans-unit.source: The size of the indent is determined by the values of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.IndentSize%2A> and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.IndentLevel%2A> properties.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.IndentLevel%2A> property represents the number of times the indent of the size specified by the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.IndentSize%2A> property is applied.
